widget.title: Sencha Device API Tester
widget.description: (Safari/Chrome browsers only): This App demonstrates various components of the FeedHenry API. App documentation is available at http://docs.feedhenry.com/wiki/Sencha_Device_API_Tester_App. Further documentation is available in the source code. The app is also on Github: https://github.com/feedhenry/FH-Sample-Sencha-Device-API-Tester
